> Hydras:
> 
> "Mirmidon, Treloss I need your assitance in order get rid a menace"

"Yes!" Myrmidon's sharp reply came over the radio, "I am on my way."

> perceptor:
> 
> "using her signature"replied the signature"the most to logical place 
> to start to search is the old Maximal base,do you want to go?"

Myrmidon looked over at Perceptor and Dark Rodimus his face grim and
dark, "Perhaps we ought to finish slaying the maximals before we go off
on any other missions. If the base is secure then they need us on the
outside!"

Without waiting for an answer Myrmidon shifted form becoming a rather
robust looking Cyber cat. With a multi-decibel growl he leaped and
began sprinting toward the exit and the battle outside!

Preston
(Myrmidon)
